'''Jung Ma'''<ref name="JQTMD">''[[Jedi Quest: The Shadow Trap]]''</ref> was a maneuver used in [[Lightsaber combat/Legends|lightsaber combat]] by [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] to perform a 360-degree spin in which power was gained for an imminent attack on the opponent.<ref name="STJM" />

Combined with ''[[Sai tok/Legends|sai tok]]'', a practitioner could slay multiple surrounding opponents with one swift stroke.<ref name="STJM" />

